               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 4r-175vb)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 4r-142v)
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 142v-156v)
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     157r-164r)
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 164va-174va)
                     I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 174va-175vb), incomplete
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
